data.route-configuration#Route configuration:
Routes can be plain strings or objects with params and auth state:
routes: [
  '/',
  '/dashboard',
  {
    path: '/profile/:id',
    params: { id: 'u_001' },
  },
  {
    path: '/admin',
    auth: 'path/to/auth-state.json',  // Playwright storageState file
  },
]

data.classifier-thresholds#Classifier thresho:
Controls how DOM elements are classified from Playwright geometry:
classifier: {
  lineHeightEstimate: 24,
  avatarSmallMax: 40,
  iconMax: 28,
  // ...
},
See Configuration for the full list.

data.customization#Customization:
Override defaults globally via skeletal.config.ts:
primitives: {
  avatar: { size: 32 },
  list: { count: 4 },
}
Or per-subtree via SkeletonProvider:
<SkeletonProvider primitives={{ avatar: { size: 32 } }}>
  <App />
</SkeletonProvider>
CSS variables (set globally or via SkeletonProvider):
:root {
  --sk-color: #e2e8f0;
  --sk-radius: 4px;
  --sk-duration: 2s;
}
